      "summary": "I think this is a pretty damn good game. it as good rates (3% for an SSR) a VERY low pity (30 pity for an SSR) and the gameplay is really fun. Ive always been a sucker for turn based combat as its my favorite genre, and i also really love roguelites/likes. So i really enjoy games like this and it hasnt gotten boring yet. However the one big problem (Mainly for PvP and such) is while the gacha is insanely generous and good for getting characters. the max dupe for a character is SIXTEEN COPYS. SIXTEEN. that is INSANE. the copys arent pushovers either. They can increase the max level of a character up to +10 and they get some general stat buffs as you get more (Also appearantly some characters get special buffs at max copys but im not 100% sure if thats true so take it with a grain of salt.)\noverall 8/10. The gameplay is fun, the art is great, and the sounds and audio is also pretty crisp. The max dups being a massive sixteen mostly really only matters for the PvP and leaderboards if your into those things. Its pretty minimal on the PvE content. (although im not super far in PvE so it could change) would recommend.",
